											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Fade up on the majesty of the outer planes. All is quiet, still, tranquil, then - something begins to happen. A new constellation begins to form in the shape of Gale's tattoo, tendrils of Netherese magic flickering around him like flashes of lightning. Pure, unbirdled power. \r\n\r\nA second symbol forms, of a similar size to Gale's. This one in the shape of Mystra's sigil, its magic the purer white/blue of the Weave. Then, we see Gale - in god-human or god-illithid form. He stands on the rippling firmament of the outer planes, Mystra before him."
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicObjects"
												},
												"val": {
