												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Human Mystra and Human/Illithid Gale adopt tense/prepared poses, confrontation brewing between them (not leading to actual combat on-screen). In the skies, both Mystra and Gale's symbols grow in intensity, becoming stormlike. Flashes of light, the rumble and crackle of magic building dangerously. Their clouds grow and exactly as they make contact with hear an almighty CRACKLE (magical storms making contact), then cut to black and hear- "
